WEBVTT

00:00:01.617 --> 00:00:05.293
U prosincu 2010.,

00:00:05.293 --> 00:00:07.110
grad Apatzingan

00:00:07.110 --> 00:00:10.262
u obalnoj državi Michoacán, u Meksiku,

00:00:10.262 --> 00:00:12.632
se probudio uz pucnjavu.

00:00:12.632 --> 00:00:14.208
Dva dana zaredom,

00:00:14.208 --> 00:00:16.626
grad je bio otvoreno bojište

00:00:16.626 --> 00:00:18.410
između federalnih snaga

00:00:18.410 --> 00:00:20.079
i dobro organizirane grupe,

00:00:20.079 --> 00:00:22.862
vjerojatno iz lokalne 
kriminalne organizacije

00:00:22.862 --> 00:00:26.234
La Familia Michoacana, 
ili obitelj Michoacan.

00:00:26.234 --> 00:00:29.384
Građani nisu samo iskusili 
neprekidnu paljbu

00:00:29.384 --> 00:00:31.804
već i eksplozije